{"tid":1375164,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【提防】霧化槍須知","createTime":"2019-07-28T03:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:31:07.000Z","uid":259980,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c6badc73f010dc0bbcc0ad7aa9ba2459cbbfeaea","tid":1375164,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XrN1PJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXrN1PJf.jpg&h=4fdefe63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日亦有記者拍攝到，有警員手持過去未有使用的大型武器戒備。<br />\n<br />\n該武器「胡椒煙霧噴射器」，是根據熱霧原理操作，利用高溫將液體<span style=\"color: orange;\">催淚</span>制劑烘煮成<span style=\"color: orange;\">氣體排出</span>。噴射器的發電機是以<span style=\"color: orange;\">脈沖式飛機引擎</span>推動等於2<span style=\"color: orange;\">6秒內噴射出100,000立方米催淚煙</span>。<br />\n<br />\n即係<span style=\"color: orange;\">指向性催淚煙</span><br />\n<br />\n有無飛機撚可以推測下<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">飛機引擎</span>推動嘅氣體<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">長寬高</span>大概係幾多<br />\n會唔會打到<span style=\"color: orange;\">大後排</span>"},{"pid":"f3b7d2e6baca6feb7daef6da09efc1800e6137ea","tid":1375164,"uid":68822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=da07109c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n\t</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7.28  中上環 下午3點 遮打花園<br />\n捍衛自由 不徹不散<br />\n五大訴求</span></strong></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />